reviewText: So many comedy's now days aim at adults only. This is one that's completely safe and teaches some good lessons for the family. Dad isn't perfect but isn't an idiot like on some many other so called family comedies. He's a bit childish at times but always means well. Thats why I love this show and look forward to the remaining seasons being available soon.
Title: According to Jim: Season 5
